data.value:
Silk offers a range of plant-based milks, with its soy milk being one of the most popular. It's fortified with calcium, vitamin D, and B12, and contains no lactose, dairy, or cholesterol. Available in unsweetened, vanilla, and chocolate flavors, it’s ideal for vegans and those with dairy intolerance.
Type of Milk: Plant-based soy milk (non-dairy)
Ideal For: Vegans and vegetarians Individuals with lactose intolerance or dairy allergies Health-conscious consumers seeking a cholesterol-free milk alternative
Ingredients: Filtered water Whole soybeans Cane sugar (varies by flavor; unsweetened variant contains no sugar) Calcium carbonate Natural flavors (in flavored varieties) Vitamin D2, Vitamin B12 Stabilizers (e.g., gellan gum, sea salt)
Storage: Store unopened cartons in a cool, dry place. Refrigerate after opening and consume within 7-10 days for best quality.
Where to buy: SM Mall of Asia Pasay City, Robinsons Supermarket Ermita, Manila
______________________________________________________________________________
Nutrition Facts (Per 240ml Serving - Unsweetened Variant): Calories: 80 kcal Protein: 7g Fat: 4g (0.5g saturated fat) Carbohydrates: 3g (0g sugar) Fiber: 1g Calcium: 450mg (45% of daily value) Vitamin D: 2.5mcg (25% of daily value) Vitamin B12: 1.2mcg (50% of daily value) Iron: 0.7mg
